```

### 17.8 Summary

| Item | Rule |
|------|------|
| YAML | Do NOT include `operation_window`, `prompt_window`, etc. |
| PageObject | Delegate to `base_page.py` public methods |
| Handler | Use `page.switch_to_operation_window()`, `click_operation_window_confirm_button()`, etc. |
